      <back>
         <div type="commentary">
            <p>On the fourth line of the stone is a problematic symbol (symbols?). As shown by Schumacher, it consists of a dotted circle with a continuing horizontal line running to the right and intersecting what appears to be a fragmentary letter or figure. If the dotted circle represents a Θ (theta), Antiochus died at the age of 9; if it is an Ο (omicron), then he died at age 70. The remaining mark looks like an opening parenthesis mark and does not yield any meaning.</p>
         </div>
